snippet.title: Love Finds A Whey - Trailer
snippet.description:
​Which cheese will you take to the summer festival? And will you achieve your dream of becoming an artisanal cheesemaker? Get ready for a romance that will make you melt. 

"Love Finds A Whey" is a short parody dating sim that was created for an Extra Life charity gaming marathon. While the gameplay isn't long, it's a cheesy good time and all proceeds will be donated to Extra Life, in support of the Children's Hospital Foundation of Manitoba.
